text: Nurfitriyana Saiman-Lantang is a retired Indonesian archer. She was born on 7 March 1962. Saiman competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, 1992 Summer Olympics, and the 1996 Summer Olympics.Nurfitriyana Saiman-LantangNurfitriyana SAIMAN == References == Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Indonesia Category:People from Jakarta
